queries.sql: SELECT `p`.`product_id`, `p`.`product_name`, COALESCE(i.current_stock, 0) as current_stock, COALESCE(i.available_stock, 0) as available_stock, `p`.`unit_price`, (COALESCE(i.current_stock, 0) * p.unit_price) as stock_value, `p`.`minimum_stock` FROM `products` `p` LEFT JOIN `inventory` `i` ON `i`.`product_id` = `p`.`product_id` AND `i`.`branch_id` = 3 WHERE `p`.`status` = 'active' ORDER BY `p`.`product_name` ASC

SELECT p.product_name, sm.created_at, SUBSTRING_INDEX(sm.notes,'=',-1) AS expires_at FROM stock_movements sm JOIN products p ON p.product_id = sm.product_id WHERE sm.branch_id = 3 AND sm.notes LIKE 'expires_at=%' AND DATE(SUBSTRING_INDEX(sm.notes,'=',-1)) BETWEEN CURDATE() AND DATE_ADD(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 14 DAY) ORDER BY expires_at ASC
